text: Aleknagik ( ; Alaqnaqiq in Central Yup'ik) is a city in the state of Alaska in the United States. It is in the Dillingham Census Area of the Unorganized Borough. In 2020, there were 211 people living there. == Sources == Category:Cities in Alaska Category:1973 establishments in the United States Category:1970s establishments in Alaska
title: Aleknagik, Alaska
